SQL-27

"Given a table containing information about bank 
deposits and withdrawals made using Paypal, 
write a query to retrieve the final account balance for each account,
taking into account all the transactions recorded in the table with 
the assumption that there are no missing transactions."

SELECT
  account_id,
  SUM(
    CASE 
      WHEN transaction_type = 'Deposit' THEN amount
      ELSE -amount END
  ) AS final_balance
FROM transactions
GROUP BY account_id;

